org.afplib.afplib

Interface GCPARC

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GCPARCImpl

    public interface GCPARC
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'GCPARC'.

    The following features are supported:

    • XCENT
    • YCENT
    • MH
    • MFR
    • START
    • SWEEP

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getGCPARC()
